headline: Eaton to announce first quarter 2025 earnings on May 2, 2025
summary: DUBLIN, April 21, 2025--Intelligent power management company Eaton (NYSE:ETN) will announce first quarter 2025 earnings on Friday, May 2, 2025, before the opening of the New York Stock Exchange. The company will host a conference call at 11 a.m. Eastern time that day to discuss first quarter 2025 earnings results with securities analysts and institutional investors.
